PWA DATA ANALYSIS - Technical Report¶

  • Created by Kevin Muhia Gathogo
  • Created on Jul 29, 2021
  • Runned on Mar 25, 2022 (feature.shape, Gives Current (x, y) x total rows/features and y the current fields)

This is a data analysis for the following Dataset in SDE 64.

DRAINAGE¶

B. Foul Sewer Water Network¶

This is an analysis/insight of the Feature classes Completeness. The report highlight the Gaps existing in the dataset in terms of empty or Null fields of each feature class.

The report aim to highlight hidden scenario such as, a feature class having a total record of 40,000 and there exists fields which have 38,000 records which are empty or not filled or null.

This might help in making decision on whether to keep those field or to delete them since they carry no information.

The report can also be used to keep track on changes in quantity of asset and the number of fields of feature classes.

The following are feature classes existing in SDE.DRG_FOUL_SEWER_NETWORK

•   Foul Sewer Lagoon & Tank
